data.description: TLast house on the left before you step onto the Trail that will take you from "Dutchtown" to Nyack! RARE chance in Dutchtown, Haverstraw NY! Unobstructed view of the Hudson River (Riparian Rights)  your search is over! This gorgeous, lovingly cared for home, gives you the story book feeling the minute you walk in there is nothing more pleasant than when you open the door, and you are in a well-built kitchen with everyday dining. There is a large living room with wood fireplace. There is a first-floor bedroom and full bath with an upstairs that has a giant loft like apartment feel (no kitchen no bath), but plumbing is roughed in the back closet and the walkout basement offers many situations that could present themselves for an extended family set up, too much to list! Coming Soon...  DID SOMEONE SAY I WANT AN AIR BNB on the "HOOK MOUNTAIN & NYACK BEACH BIKEWAY!!!
